api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://yahoo-finance15.p.rapidapi.com/api/yahoo/qu/quote/AAPL,MSFT"

            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "yahoo-finance15.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
